There are several steps you should do.

1. Download cmake (sudo apt-get install cmake)

2. Set up your .bash_profile
create .bash_profile at your home directory
export PATH=$PATH:/home/kyushick/work/svn_work/CGO_Project/CGO_LC3b_13f/llvm/Release+Asserts/bin
and save it and exit. then source it(source .bash_profile)

3. go to the gitworkingdir/llvm/test

4. mkdir cmake_debug_build

5. cd cmake_debug_build

6. cmake -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=clang++ -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER=clang -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -G "Unix Makefiles" ../src/

7. That's it.
